cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with understanding the 3-dimensional structure of the world, which is a core challenge in computer vision. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper mentions that the proposed datasets are inspired by real-world robotics. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is likely as the paper proposes a new attention mechanism for neural rendering. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is likely as the paper deals with learning an implicit 3D model using neural rendering approaches. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics) is also likely as the paper deals with rendering scenes from arbitrary viewpoints.
